= 1920 Fasci Congress

The *Fasci Italiani di Combattimento*, known also as the Fasci was formed in March and have begun their second congress to decide the party's agenda. [? if not mussolini_jailed :It seems all but confirmed that Benito Mussolini will come out on top once again. ?][? if mussolini_jailed: With Mussolini in jail, the organisation's future is uncertain. ?]

